00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:23,520
 under the sun, trying to find something that won't just be hevel.

121
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,640
 Indulgence, hevel.

122
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,560
 Wisdom, hevel.

123
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,280
 Work, hevel.

124
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,280
 Money, hevel.

125
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,280
 Honour, hevel.

