00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,980
 die.

184
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:36,200
 Now I think this really captures the heart of the issue.

185
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:40,360
 We can worry about, plan around or put off the idea of death.

